"smart_blocks:Sessões/2026-04-13.md#Sessões — 2026-04-13#Em linguagem simples --- ### O que eu fiz Coloquei um **alarme automático** dentro do Claude Code. Toda vez que eu termino de responder, esse alarme dispara e roda um programinha que eu criei. Esse programinha pega tudo que aconteceu na conversa e escreve num arquivo do Obsidian. Você não faz nada. Acontece sozinho. --- ### Como funciona Imagina assim: > Você fala comigo → Eu respondo → **Automaticamente**, a conversa é salva no Obsidian → Você fala de novo → Eu respondo → **Salva de novo** → e assim por diante Cada vez que salva, **substitui** o que tinha antes pelo estado mais atual. Entã…": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"64mr7x","at":1776087923170},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06752366,0.0263791,0.03983725,-0.00977248,0.01010757,-0.02451291,-0.00096013,0.08473983,-0.0186444,0.03246739,-0.03335711,-0.06605282,-0.0267268,0.02021729,0.0337218,0.0162294,0.02381318,0.01518584,0.00827159,-0.01024247,0.1398232,-0.01822084,0.01010329,-0.02152256,-0.0234299,-0.00969306,0.00765988,-0.0077342,-0.03589396,-0.17850834,0.04286966,0.00878054,0.0456649,-0.04598992,-0.00942491,-0.00470448,-0.02322178,-0.03660738,-0.05739335,0.03432272,-0.03588055,0.05799337,0.01610983,-0.02906202,-0.03384583,-0.09416351,-0.01079504,0.00640318,-0.00842808,-0.0251287,0.02010822,-0.01068876,-0.0248596,-0.00243049,-0.01449489,-0.01219814,0.04907002,0.03472665,0.04274662,0.056896,0.03878794,-0.02804348,-0.22284128,0.08127872,-0.02017244,0.04106189,-0.03128323,-0.00957698,0.00229468,0.02914272,-0.04381477,0.02372116,0.04812284,0.06285275,0.0498393,-0.01140221,0.00113016,-0.05206861,-0.04615396,-0.01896808,-0.01144228,0.02773797,-0.01136392,-0.02013762,-0.03937046,-0.00430578,0.04947507,0.00323889,0.05509207,0.00508596,-0.08877856,0.0110982,0.07824989,0.05655302,0.02856885,-0.02713027,0.00805853,0.00879783,-0.06336651,0.10299432,0.02749003,-0.00679204,0.04235242,-0.01857661,0.12280152,-0.01454928,0.00994723,-0.07892682,-0.0