"smart_blocks:Sessões/2026-04-13.md#Diagnóstico Completo — Sistema de Auto-Save de Sessões --- ## O QUE FIZEMOS HOJE ### Problema identificado Você perdia contexto toda vez que abria uma nova sessão com qualquer ferramenta de IA. Não havia memória persistente entre conversas. O objetivo: salvar automaticamente tudo no Obsidian, sem nenhum comando manual. ### Ferramentas cobertas | Ferramenta | Conta | Método de captura | |---|---|---| | Claude | Conta 1 (`claude`) | Hooks nativos (Stop + PostToolUse) | | Claude Nova | Conta 2 (`claude-nova`) | Hooks nativos (Stop + PostToolUse) | | Codex (OpenAI) | — | File watcher em `rollout…": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1lmdk8v","at":1776112617185},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05224924,0.06872064,0.05262143,-0.02037747,0.05637062,-0.01753039,0.0184573,0.08544443,-0.00976893,-0.01832822,-0.0355036,-0.07706589,-0.00725199,0.06349321,0.00994773,0.0340273,-0.02761578,0.05593529,0.01412386,0.02518942,0.10677022,-0.02023061,-0.00965197,-0.05968892,-0.00818115,0.03027632,0.02264134,0.00936416,-0.02138089,-0.21091929,0.00651697,-0.00311799,-0.02440734,-0.03181935,-0.03543623,0.01867267,-0.02948102,-0.04236263,-0.00837831,0.06791278,-0.0088108,0.02121933,-0.05992496,-0.00815109,-0.02958058,-0.02438866,0.05319679,-0.01019359,0.00805544,-0.03231012,-0.00743566,-0.01351378,0.00644952,-0.00270869,-0.01863457,0.01678087,0.02767894,0.02761985,0.0411509,0.03896872,0.05910848,0.02887159,-0.24993227,0.02301364,0.02109289,-0.00274068,-0.04348555,-0.00192714,-0.02723729,-0.00318553,-0.0282406,0.01193212,0.03521433,0.09100848,0.00714878,0.01259424,0.01849907,-0.04117098,-0.05538533,-0.00472126,0.00481882,0.0584523,-0.01085591,-0.00768498,-0.02743836,-0.03293427,0.03765162,-0.02586493,0.03376065,-0.02134867,-0.05789112,0.01361007,0.07544289,0.04788273,-0.01764394,0.01165266,-0.00091707,0.04772919,-0.00313806,0.09248203,0.03084906,-0.01070834,0.04093522,-0.03276708,0.04144013,0.0029473,-0.0208562,-0.08210515,-0.03738725,0.03