"smart_blocks:Sessões/2026-04-13.md#Sessões — 2026-04-13#Resumo do que o Grok respondeu ### GitHub App — mudança de plano Ele voltou atrás na própria recomendação. GitHub App não é plug-and-play no Obsidian Git (token expira em 8h). **Nova recomendação: Git Credential Manager (GCM)** — já vem no Git for Windows, autentica via OAuth no navegador, armazena no Windows Credential Manager, não expira. Você faz isso manualmente em 5 minutos agora ou depois da implementação. Não muda nada no código. Passos: 1. Confirmar que Git for Windows está instalado com GCM 2. `git config --global credential.helper manager` 3. No Obsidian Git: deixar o campo de tok…": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1n0r1lh","at":1776113033137},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02475693,0.01643927,0.07621476,-0.03604589,-0.02317638,-0.021524,-0.04611127,0.04228995,-0.0378964,0.00922852,-0.02070313,-0.0973621,-0.03955062,0.02585913,0.03276563,-0.04515001,0.00194527,0.0191803,0.00367654,-0.03714782,0.1065692,-0.04873321,0.02409021,-0.06106412,-0.0023759,-0.02034053,-0.08207851,-0.03094733,-0.08557459,-0.16228895,-0.01952117,-0.01351722,-0.01356301,0.0579645,-0.00953665,-0.00553276,-0.03355373,-0.00155152,-0.10782216,0.04942679,0.0155424,0.01453959,-0.03794489,0.00943543,-0.00355924,-0.09944336,-0.04028071,-0.03609522,-0.00347104,-0.03061192,0.03500032,0.01324619,-0.02300416,0.02680485,-0.02859175,0.02382859,0.05016845,0.00809204,0.07531492,0.04168929,0.05401764,0.01679997,-0.20850082,0.07487461,0.00053661,0.04692144,-0.02934484,-0.04091606,-0.0012926,0.013992,-0.01739783,0.00472514,-0.00129348,0.02963459,0.03250185,0.01344942,-0.00101728,0.03206417,-0.03131836,-0.0213478,-0.01958738,0.10895108,0.00524094,-0.01673221,-0.03914013,-0.07298636,-0.00764579,0.01025401,0.01580737,-0.02733972,-0.02101921,-0.01554846,0.08957885,0.03500373,-0.01989515,-0.01364348,0.01533042,0.05296917,-0.08520638,0.12693216,-0.0467945,-0.0189531,-0.03096056,-0.01542165,0.11184319,0.03231097,0.00119462,-0.0381106